Delicious! Imagine a potato salad with no onion that tastes good. This goes together quickly and does not need time to chill for flavors to meld. I peel and cube potatoes before I boil them to make the cooking speed up and to make them easy to handle. I also reduce the eggs to two if I don't have three and can't see much difference.

